{"tid":2034824,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"平時IDOL送比人D簽名專輯其實會點處理??","createTime":"2020-05-25T13:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T10:12:06.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c713f28d5513a7ef793a532fcba72800f5e24e35","tid":2034824,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:04:12.000Z","msg":"南韓清新女團Oh My Girl於2015年成軍出道，她們去年參與實境秀《QUEENDOM》一舉成名，終於打開知名度，人氣扶搖直上，成為近期備受討論的女團。怎料，韓媒25日爆出一則她們送給前輩Lovelyz的專輯遭拿到二手拍賣競標，專輯上還有成員親自寫下的文字與簽名，立刻引來各方議論，Lovelyz經紀公司Woollim娛樂也憤恨地出面表示專輯遭偷走，目前已報警處理。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4898/d4898879.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4898%2Fd4898879.jpg&h=0d239a0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼ Oh My Girl親筆簽給Lovelyz的專輯出現在網路上拍賣。（圖／翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4898/d4898880.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4898%2Fd4898880.jpg&h=cdd54ef5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOh My Girl過去發行第二張迷你專輯《CLOSER》，近日被發現出現在中古拍賣網站，令歌迷最為震驚的是，該專輯其實是她們送給前輩Lovelyz的親簽CD，上面清楚寫著「TO Lovelyz前輩，這次推出的歌曲《A-CHU》很清新又活潑，我們這次也出了新歌《CLOSER》希望多多喜愛，會一直成為努力地Oh My Girl。」親簽專輯出現在中古拍賣網站，立刻引起議論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4898/d4898892.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4898%2Fd4898892.jpg&h=988b5dcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Lovelyz所屬經紀公司Woollim娛樂緊急報警，認為公司裡出現小偷。（圖／翻攝自Lovelyz臉書）<br />\n<br />\n對此，Lovelyz所屬經紀公司Woollim娛樂鄭重地發出聲明，警告網站上販賣旗下藝人（Lovelyz）的所有物為非法行為，他們強調一直以來都很妥善保管後輩、前輩送來的簽名CD，絕對不可能送給別人，因此判定該張專輯出現在中古拍賣網站應是遭偷走了，目前已報警處理，並希望可以盡快拿回該張專輯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成件事好尷尬"},{"pid":"f50162e813dcb84cd1bbce80dab65be75784d333","tid":2034824,"uid":33359,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:04:57.000Z","msg":"送禮勤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0690e928f627734f3e8c4d60272867ddf16672d","tid":2034824,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f50162e813dcb84cd1bbce80dab65be75784d333","tid":2034824,"uid":33359,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:04:57.000Z","msg":"送禮勤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撚夠未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd9606d4d2f71c11a516f4795b66008fe34eb12","tid":2034824,"uid":198607,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:09:01.000Z","msg":"▲Lovelyz所屬經紀公司Woollim娛樂緊急報警，<span style=\"color: red;\">認為公司裡出現小偷</span>。<br />\n<br />\n邊隻賊仔咁蠱惑 唔偷錢走去偷專<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5f713ff1932b4d5c54f6ef55127460d853eba6","tid":2034824,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7fd9606d4d2f71c11a516f4795b66008fe34eb12","tid":2034824,"uid":198607,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:09:01.000Z","msg":"▲Lovelyz所屬經紀公司Woollim娛樂緊急報警，<span style=\"color: red;\">認為公司裡出現小偷</span>。<br />\n<br />\n邊隻賊仔咁蠱惑 唔偷錢走去偷專<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T13:11:55.000Z","msg":"貪個幾舊水<im